<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause"?><clause id="_a95bbab7-1ce7-4f30-82a5-d3944416b267" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NT"><sptc>13.7.2</sptc><title id="_e84e1677-62f4-4227-ac2f-8a54e35f71e1">Insulation of services</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_380a6d0d-9717-44ce-b23b-d2ac48fcc01a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a26e111c-0042-42e4-a9e8-62697a0bea17">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Thermal insulation for central heating water <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1399_0.5.0.xml#_c2a4355b-831c-4629-a13d-2c18c2a4ae92" id="_2cf604a0-79fc-4749-b7c4-7826e32dd70f" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">piping</xref> and heating and cooling ductwork must be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e423e6cc-aed8-4ce4-a946-00cd30e39348">protected against the effects of weather and sunlight; and</li><li id="_a6a0f0e2-6f33-483a-a01a-d6366cd24e42">able to withstand the temperatures within the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1399_0.5.0.xml#_c2a4355b-831c-4629-a13d-2c18c2a4ae92" id="_8141fe87-811c-4b7f-978c-65053c725f14" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">piping</xref> or ductwork.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_68957fe1-bb1e-45d3-86d7-28e9a55b5043"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>The central heating water <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1399_0.5.0.xml#_c2a4355b-831c-4629-a13d-2c18c2a4ae92" id="_76a25fdf-a9dc-4ddf-ad93-13b0088bb393" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">piping</xref> provisions apply to systems designed to heat the building via water, such as a hydronic heating system.</p></callout></clause>